The paper deals with instance segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed approach involves learning from a single video without human annotation, which suggests the use of machine learning techniques such as deep learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of structured likelihood and illumination transformation, which are related to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
